Visit http://umeboshi-fireteam.no.de to try it out.

One of the HTML demos developed to showcase what can be done using the Umeboshi Server to enable page-communication and sliceable apps.

The project started as a hack entry for the Node.js Knockout on August of 2010. 

And if you want to help us, please review/vote on our entry at http://nodeknockout.com/teams/umeboshi-fireteam and make sure you vote/review 5 other submissions as well to make your vote count :)

Thanks for watching!